features: Made in the USA: Made of durable paper material, our 1-ply paper napkins for dinner are strong and absorbent. Great for everyday use, birthday parties, picnics, barbecues, camping, and more!
Disposable: Our white dinner napkins are perfect for cleaning up trivial spills and messes. No need to worry about cleanup - simply toss them in the trash when you’re done.

Classic White Napkins: Our chic, white disposable napkins easily blend in with any home decor. Use our napkins to complete your place setting for dinner. They’re also great for commercial use like catering events, restaurants, wedding venues, and more.
Arts & Crafts: Our paper napkins are undecorated with a cute floral, printed pattern making them a great choice for crafts, DIY projects, and paper mache. The possibilities are endless!
Great Value Pack: Our value pack comes with 500 1-Ply, 12” x 12” white napkins. Order yours today!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They do the job
reviews.reviewText: These are thin, one-ply, very basic napkins. Good for wiping crumbs, but wiping liquids not so much.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Not as absorbent as I would like

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars OK - product post shows 2 packs of 500 - but they ship 1 pack of 1000
reviews.reviewText: The napkins are OK. A little thin, but they work as lunch napkins.The product photo is misleading, though. It shows 2 packs of 500 but they ship 1 pack of 1000.I picked this product specifically because I was stocking two different break rooms and was planning to put 1 package in each.(Not a huge deal, I just need to figure out how to contain the napkins not actively in dispensers since I can't just leave them in the original packaging as I'd planned to. Because they are so light, they tend to blow around anytime a cabinet door is opened instead of just staying neatly in a stack like other napkins might.)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Napkins are wonderful
reviews.reviewText: They are great, napkins, wonderful texture. What can you say about napkins? They’re inexpensive and good thank you JOE.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really love these napkins. I purchased them because I thought it was a good economically priced package. I am amazed at how soft they are. All my friends love them and asked where I got them. I will definitely be buying them again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Thin thin not very good, not good for dinner
reviews.reviewText: They say online they are dinner napkins, but when they arrive they say Luncheon. These are so thin, not good at all unless you're eating a piece of toast .

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Hi previous to purchasing this, I was buying them from the grocery store. Amazon’s price is competitive, napkins are soft and durable. And didn’t need to leave the couch to purchase them. Highly recommend them
